<paragraph id="C0F80827F93F3A04239F9A4E2E43A754" pageId="5" pageNumber="8">
Figure 7. Comparative views of male genitalia: Left: 
<taxonomicName id="5E2AAE274CD24B07F1631E162F63CCEF" authority="Packard, 1864" authorityName="Packard" authorityYear="1864" class="Insecta" family="Apatelodidae" genus="Apatelodes" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Apatelodes chalupae" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="5" pageNumber="8" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="chalupae">Apatelodes chalupae</taxonomicName>
(H1380) Right: 
<taxonomicName id="6AAB6E50F3BDBF0EE4657896830E43F9" authority="Packard, 1864" authorityName="Packard" authorityYear="1864" class="Insecta" family="Apatelodidae" genus="Apatelodes" higherTaxonomySource="GBIF" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Apatelodes navarroi" order="Lepidoptera" pageId="5" pageNumber="8" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="navarroi">Apatelodes navarroi</taxonomicName>
(H1381).
</paragraph>
</caption>
</subSubSection>
